Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.59,0:00:07.34,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,最终还是下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.22,0:00:11.89,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,但是没想到 一个观众也没有来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.30,0:00:15.60,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,明明在网上发布好了公告的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.39,0:00:20.60,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.35,0:00:22.56,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,被摆了一道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.77,0:00:23.86,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,摆了一道?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.40,0:00:27.36,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,网页上的通知 被人篡改了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.36,0:00:30.65,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,有人黑了我们的网站改掉了通知
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.70,0:00:35.33,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,黑客…情况不乐观啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.45,0:00:37.95,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,谁会做这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.25,0:00:51.88,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,都能想象他们慌乱的样子 总理
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.59,0:00:53.76,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,再加上这种天气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.76,0:00:57.64,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,就算运气好 有人去了会场
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.31,0:01:00.73,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,也算不上什么演唱会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.35,0:01:03.65,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,真是场及时雨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.48,0:01:10.15,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这次可不会让你们为所欲为了 丫头片子们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.32,0:01:15.49,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,别想再翻身了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.58,0:01:20.79,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,要怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.91,0:01:22.12,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,还能怎能办…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.50,0:01:23.92,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,就算现在重新发布公告…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.92,0:01:26.38,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,像这样的雨天 没人会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.88,0:01:28.67,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,等等 星菜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.38,0:01:33.43,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,冰凉的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.30,0:01:37.35,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,但很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.22,0:01:41.73,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,在雨中唱歌不也挺好的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.64,0:01:46.15,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我说你们二位 现在没有观众啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.44,0:01:48.77,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这样你们还想继续演唱会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.23,0:01:52.44,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,因为我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.37,0:01:58.37,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是偶像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.70,0:02:01.49,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,要把歌声传递给大家!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.87,0:02:03.71,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,说的好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.00,0:02:05.71,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,可是下这么大的雨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.04,0:02:07.29,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,万一感冒的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.42,0:02:09.75,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,撇去那个 现在也没观众啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.84,0:02:13.84,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,没观众的话 就想办法让他们来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.55,0:02:17.80,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,可别小瞧偶像哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.89,0:02:32.14,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这是什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.60,0:02:33.97,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,好像听过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.31,0:02:37.39,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,诶 是那首歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.06,0:02:39.60,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,WITH的《START UP, DREAM!!》
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.77,0:02:41.69,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,今天好像是有演唱会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.19,0:02:43.78,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不是说中止了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.57,0:02:45.49,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那这歌是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.74,0:02:49.16,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这歌好像是从野外舞台那边传来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.57,0:02:51.07,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,走吧走吧 看看去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.62,0:02:57.37,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.96,0:02:59.71,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,总觉的有点厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.87,0:03:01.08,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,超厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.36,0:03:25.44,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,她们俩到底在想什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.94,0:03:28.61,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这要是被发现了肯定会有大麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.95,0:03:31.82,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,说不定可能会被剥夺议员资格
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.32,0:03:36.54,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,现在担心这个 为时已晚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.16,0:03:39.71,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,终于开始了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.13,0:03:43.92,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,小梅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.17,0:03:45.92,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,小梅 樱井议员
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.75,0:03:47.84,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,桂山议员
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.59,0:03:49.88,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不好了 看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.63,0:03:52.05,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,请你看下这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.43,0:03:57.60,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.85,0:03:59.73,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.31,0:04:02.60,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你们在看什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.10,0:04:05.57,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,啊 这是我的手机
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.86,0:04:07.73,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,之前的那位姐姐在唱歌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.95,0:04:11.28,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.61,0:04:12.78,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,简直是大新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.99,0:04:15.99,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,知道了 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.91,0:04:20.96,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,其他偶像议员好像也行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.62,0:04:22.29,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.83,0:04:25.59,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不用担心 已经有所准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.25,0:04:28.46,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,他们应该是打算在演唱会上汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.09,0:04:32.30,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,抵达不了会场的话也就没意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.76,0:04:35.43,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不知天高地厚的丫头片子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.22,0:04:42.02,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不到预想的人数啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.77,0:04:47.23,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,果然 这场演唱会从开始就失败了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.69,0:04:51.53,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,夏月 静 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.53,0:04:55.28,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我们不是独自在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:04.37,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,堵车是没办法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:07.59,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,但怎么觉得老在一个地方转啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.92,0:05:12.01,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,十分抱歉 高速公路出口好像关闭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.55,0:05:15.55,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,啊 这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.77,0:05:23.69,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,各位乘客 现播送一条通知
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.56,0:05:26.35,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,由于前方的转辙器发生故障
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.81,0:05:28.77,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,现在是紧急停车
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.40,0:05:32.40,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,目前尚未确定何时重新发车
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.49,0:05:38.57,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.03,0:05:40.54,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.04,0:05:41.58,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.70,0:05:44.50,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.87,0:05:50.13,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,怎么回事 没看见吗 当然是在休息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.42,0:05:52.42,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,别碍事 快把车开走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.88,0:05:54.38,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我们都过不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.13,0:05:58.68,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,嗯 你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.85,0:06:01.56,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,今天我的耳朵放假
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.35,0:06:04.56,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,怎么办 樱井议员
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.56,0:06:11.15,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,啊 堵车…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.11,0:06:12.90,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,没路了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.74,0:06:22.37,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,看好了 大浪来喽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.87,0:06:24.79,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,走开 蠢货 别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.79,0:06:26.66,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.66,0:06:27.37,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.37,0:06:29.25,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,上啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.80,0:06:36.42,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.01,0:06:38.43,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.89,0:06:45.02,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,还好我个子矮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.61,0:06:52.69,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,伽里亚议员
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.07,0:06:54.07,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,没受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.48,0:06:55.11,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.44,0:06:56.24,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.53,0:07:03.33,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,没有更好的办法了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.24,0:07:06.41,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这样一点也不Cosmic
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.83,0:07:09.42,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,可笑 黑暗无所畏惧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.83,0:07:12.38,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,正是黑暗给予我们力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.97,0:07:19.43,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你们搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.76,0:07:21.26,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,快让我们过去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.59,0:07:22.43,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.85,0:07:25.43,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不想受伤的话就乖乖回家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.52,0:07:26.31,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.85,0:07:28.31,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,别让我说第二次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.68,0:07:29.69,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不想受伤就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.40,0:07:36.86,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,动刀子可不好啊 小子们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:39.74,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你们还算是男人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.78,0:07:42.95,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,古里议员…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.53,0:07:46.29,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这里交给我们 你们快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.91,0:07:47.33,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.45,0:07:50.71,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,偶尔也让我耍耍帅嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.21,0:07:52.63,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,快走吧 千夏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.13,0:07:53.63,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.38,0:07:56.84,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,古里议员 谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.72,0:08:06.06,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,让你们明白为难我们的偶像议员有什么下场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.10,0:08:12.02,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,樱子小姐 准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.52,0:08:12.85,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.40,0:08:14.31,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.52,0:08:15.15,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.33,0:08:30.54,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,无论遇到什么困难 我们都不会输
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.25,0:08:35.50,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,为了大家 为了大家的笑容而歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.09,0:08:39.76,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,为了什么 为了谁歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.21,0:08:41.92,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,竟然会变得这么开心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.51,0:08:43.13,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,传递到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.51,0:08:44.22,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,传递到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.51,0:08:46.39,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,传递到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.14,0:08:54.65,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,糟了 总理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.10,0:08:58.11,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,偶像议员和一般市民突破了防线
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.40,0:09:01.53,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,陆续到达会场了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.45,0:09:04.16,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,总理?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.95,0:09:07.16,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这可是千载难逢的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.79,0:09:16.04,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我亲自去前线指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.56,0:09:22.94,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,感谢大家冒雨前来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.07,0:09:24.15,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.70,0:09:28.03,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,观众正一点点聚集
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:33.00,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,可是…想要改变这个现状 还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.21,0:09:41.42,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.30,0:09:44.97,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,现在放弃还太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.42,0:09:47.97,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这不只是女主角党的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.64,0:09:51.89,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,别忘了还有我们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.52,0:09:54.77,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.52,0:10:00.86,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,各位贵安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.61,0:10:05.61,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我的登场方式会不会太引人注目了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.99,0:10:07.32,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,抱歉我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.57,0:10:09.45,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,请让我也加入吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.95,0:10:11.78,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,快给我让开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.62,0:10:16.71,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,竟敢站在掌控黑暗力量的我头上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.67,0:10:21.92,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,让你尝尝报应
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.67,0:10:24.84,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,够啦 快出去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.88,0:10:26.42,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,正在兴头上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.51,0:10:29.18,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,为什么你会随身携带这种诡异的道具啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.22,0:10:30.14,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,工作需要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.68,0:10:34.22,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,大家…怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.64,0:10:36.14,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,还需要问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.89,0:10:37.77,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,瑞希
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.14,0:10:40.90,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,虽然我们的理念和政党不同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.36,0:10:43.27,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,但心中所盼是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.15,0:10:47.28,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这是我们偶像议员的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.07,0:10:52.62,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,夏月
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.25,0:11:00.33,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.54,0:11:04.13,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,能再次和静一起唱歌 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.80,0:11:07.01,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,因为有夏月在我才能歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.63,0:11:09.30,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我们一起努力到最后吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.84,0:11:10.30,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.84,0:11:13.05,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我们也会一起战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.97,0:11:16.14,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,大家…你们的服饰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.72,0:11:19.44,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,可不能只让你们两个出风头
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.85,0:11:21.98,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,星菜 你太见外了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.23,0:11:24.32,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我们是同一战线的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.52,0:11:27.32,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,夏月 我们一起让这里变成最棒的舞台吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.57,0:11:30.78,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,没错 希望一起登上三星级舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.53,0:11:37.08,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这个还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.12,0:11:39.58,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.79,0:11:43.21,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,别误会 我还没有认同你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.88,0:11:47.13,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,总有一天 我会凭实力占据你的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.88,0:11:49.05,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,千夏…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.85,0:12:38.93,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这是什么鬼!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.43,0:12:41.31,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这样的话不就不能搞事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.10,0:12:43.94,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,既然这样强制排除她们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.56,0:12:48.69,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,把偶像议员和聚集的观众全部赶走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.23,0:12:52.03,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,有抵抗的直接逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.70,0:12:53.57,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,听懂了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.95,0:12:56.74,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.12,0:12:58.74,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,全员 向后转
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.83,0:13:02.62,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你们在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.87,0:13:04.46,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,要赶走的是她们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.71,0:13:06.13,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.58,0:13:08.79,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,听不到我的命令吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.96,0:13:10.13,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,听不见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.25,0:13:11.84,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,什么 是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.26,0:13:14.93,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,没人会听你的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.38,0:13:16.51,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.93,0:13:19.10,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我是这里的负责人 小野寺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.47,0:13:23.73,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,多亏了星菜议员的功绩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.31,0:13:26.94,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,荣升转进了总部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.23,0:13:29.69,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你是不是想被炒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.77,0:13:31.98,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,原先生 可不能乱说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.74,0:13:37.53,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,就算是长官 也没有权利随便开除公务员
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.82,0:13:39.45,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你是…鹭宫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.78,0:13:43.33,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,就是啊 只是办个演唱会而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.54,0:13:47.75,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,随意干涉才是侵犯了言论自由
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.08,0:13:49.75,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,一起享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.54,0:13:54.84,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,而且原本偶像议员禁止法就有不合理的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.30,0:14:00.10,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,猫岛 古里 桂山 还有伽里亚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.39,0:14:02.64,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你们这群混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.07,0:15:02.37,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,总理 还是有大量观众从车站进入
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.95,0:15:04.87,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,为什么会有这么多人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.08,0:15:07.58,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,既然这样只能联系警察局长官了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.58,0:15:10.92,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不 还是命令自卫队出动维护治安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.13,0:15:13.84,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,把那群小丫头统统除掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.67,0:15:19.72,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,总理?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.31,0:15:33.06,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,她们不是偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.48,0:15:36.73,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是偶像议员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.91,0:15:44.74,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,好啊 那我就接受你们的挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.33,0:16:35.67,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,为什么各位会…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.84,0:16:38.50,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,还用问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.21,0:16:43.76,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,因为我觉的这是我们现在应该做的事…仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.30,0:16:47.18,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,可你们不是还没认同我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.64,0:16:51.48,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,确实比不上三日月神乐那个时代
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.81,0:16:53.81,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,所以才要继续奔跑前进
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.52,0:16:58.15,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,直到能超越我们的那天为止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.48,0:17:00.40,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我们都会是挡在你们面前的高山
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.49,0:17:14.92,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,非常感谢今天来这里听我们唱歌的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.99,0:17:53.04,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,前些日子 偶像议员举办的演唱会给社会带来了巨大的冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.62,0:17:55.04,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我作为一名政治家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.29,0:17:57.00,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不 作为总理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.17,0:17:59.42,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不能听之任之
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.04,0:18:05.05,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这个国家的国民对我们政治家抱有怎样的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.55,0:18:06.59,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我想听听回答
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.93,0:18:09.43,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我作为总理宣布
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.89,0:18:15.85,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,解散议会 举行大选
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.44,0:18:17.85,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,果然是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.94,0:18:24.15,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,举行大选 看来是下定决心了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.32,0:18:26.07,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,没事的 不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.99,0:18:29.49,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,只要和静在一起 做什么都能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.33,0:18:33.04,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.16,0:18:39.00,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,好了 你们两个都鼓起干劲来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.37,0:18:39.88,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.81,0:20:26.52,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,夏月 不开电视看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.98,0:20:28.32,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.53,0:20:31.45,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,看选举速报只会更紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.78,0:20:34.16,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,而且该做的都做了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.66,0:20:36.78,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,真的一点也没变啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.45,0:20:38.49,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.99,0:20:40.91,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,来 随便吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.41,0:20:44.67,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,真棒 是奶奶做的饭团
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.67,0:20:45.42,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.96,0:20:46.50,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.21,0:20:48.92,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,感觉比平时的大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.17,0:20:50.01,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.21,0:20:51.67,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,鼓起干劲捏的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.97,0:20:54.09,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,来 三平也别客气 随便吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.51,0:20:54.97,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.64,0:20:57.80,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.93,0:21:00.52,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.86,0:21:08.86,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你好 我是星菜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.57,0:21:11.57,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是的 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.28,0:21:15.28,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,什么 真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.95,0:21:17.28,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.75,0:21:27.96,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.97,0:21:36.13,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你在感伤个什么劲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.30,0:21:39.89,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我们的战斗才刚刚开始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.39,0:21:43.77,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,抱歉 感觉再次回来有点感动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.10,0:21:45.27,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不也挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.89,0:21:50.98,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不过各位偶像议员一个没少都再次当选
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.40,0:21:52.36,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.65,0:21:54.03,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.40,0:21:57.41,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,嗯 马上就能在会议厅看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.41,0:21:58.82,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,快走吧 静
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.03,0:22:00.08,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,急什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.12,0:22:02.74,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,跟学校一样 不能在走廊乱跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.12,0:22:04.58,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我知道的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.96,0:22:07.62,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,总理
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.83,0:22:10.67,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,看来顺利当选了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.09,0:22:13.21,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,先恭喜一下你们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.88,0:22:16.80,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不过我的信念是不会改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.34,0:22:19.93,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,国会议员不需要表演
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.43,0:22:23.77,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,作为议员 只要为国政献身
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.10,0:22:30.31,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,如果你们还要在自己坚信的道路上前进的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.65,0:22:33.23,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,就尽管放马过来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.69,0:22:35.49,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我会随时接受挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.20,0:22:45.04,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,可不要输给他了 夏月
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.25,0:22:47.62,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这可是我们的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.46,0:22:49.42,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.96,0:22:53.84,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,让大家露出笑容 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.84,0:22:56.55,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.47,0:23:43.30,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我是出生在福冈的偶像议员 鬼丸静
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.60,0:23:45.76,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,多亏了大家的声援我才能走到这里
